Insider Activity


Individual




Vicki L. Avril



Ms. Vicki L. Avril is Independent Director at Global Brass & Copper Holdings, Inc. and Independent Director at Greif, Inc. She is on the Board of Directors at Commercial Metals Co., Global Brass & Copper Holdings, Inc., and Greif, Inc.
Ms. Avril was previously employed as President & Chief Executive Officer by TMK IPSCO, Chief Financial Officer & Senior Vice President by Wallace Computer Services, Inc., a Principal by Inland Steel Industries, Inc., and Senior Vice President-Tubular & General Manager by IPSCO, Inc.
She received her undergraduate degree from the University of Illinois and an MBA from The University of Chicago.



